result.title: Battle #1'
result.content:
Salam conteste avval ba tavaoh be moshkelati ke bara y bache ha pish oomad va ma fekr kardim momkene sherkat konande kam dashte bashe avaz shod.

conteste jadidi ke gozashte shode shamele 5 soale az Gym ke besiar amoozandas va chanta az soalash ham sabk marhale 3 i dare omidvaram ke betunin sherkat konin va agaram natoonestid hatman be soorate Virtual contest ro bedin miarze ;-)

contest raase saate 5 shoroo mishe va zamani ke baray contest dar nazar gerefte shode 2:30 saate pas tamame saayetoono bokonin ke soala y bishtari ro hal konin

Cya in battlefield! ;)
